<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>421</hymn_number>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vancung khua chungah kan hawi le hla an sa, A kan Khamhbawi a min kha
 an thangthat cio, Vawleicung sifah retheihnak an philh cang, Mithiang mi
 nih lunglawmhnak hla thar an sa.

[C1]
   Bawipa thangthat u, (Bawipa thangthat u) Kal-va-ry tlang a thimi kha
   (thimi kha) Bawipa thangthat u, (Bawipa thangthat u), Thihnak a tei, a
   nung than cang.

[V2]
 A zaangfahnak thangthat awk hla a tling ko, A zummi caah thachin
 nganbik a si. Kan Bawipa thihnak le thawhthan nak thawngin, Pathian sinah
 a zungzal in kan um lai.

[C2]
   Bawipa thangthat u, (Bawipa thangthat u) Kal-va-ry tlang a thimi kha
   (thimi kha) Bawipa thangthat u, (Bawipa thangthat u), Thihnak a tei, a
   nung than cang.

[V3]
 Nihin a thi in a tawl lomi vialte, Ahohmanh, khi hla thar an sa kho
 lai lo. A sualmi ngaihthiam awkah a kan zaangfah, Lawmhnak he a zungzal
 in hla kan sa lai.

[C3]
   Bawipa thangthat u, (Bawipa thangthat u) Kal-va-ry tlang a thimi kha
   (thimi kha) Bawipa thangthat u, (Bawipa thangthat u), Thihnak a tei, a
   nung than cang.</lyrics>
<title>HLA THAR AN SA CH421</title>
</song>